    <h3>Outcomes</h3>
    <p>Our design and product management processes had tremendous success. Stakeholder, developers, and executives enjoyed being a part of the process early on; our off-shore team benefited from our functional prototypes which reduced churn. All in all, we were able to successfully release major updates quarterly with smaller enhancements throughout the cycle.</p>
    
